{"tid":2039414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國駐加拿大總領事館的外牆被塗鴉","createTime":"2020-05-28T04:12:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T04:31:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd756b507d49d1338c23167fe8c75e8e1e2f9f0f","tid":2039414,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:12:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.singtao.ca/wp-content/uploads/rtnews/2020/05/AAE97929-729F-445F-8CE5-2F22900F8770.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.singtao.ca%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Frtnews%2F2020%2F05%2FAAE97929-729F-445F-8CE5-2F22900F8770.jpeg&h=b8ce5a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國駐卡加利總領事館外牆遭塗鴉破壞，內容涉及仇恨言論，警方通過監控視頻已確定有三人涉案，正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據CTV報道，位於卡加利市中心的中國駐卡加利總領事館外牆，周三早晨出現塗鴉， 文字內容包括「 中國病毒」（China Virus）及其他侮辱性字眼。"},{"pid":"438f9eb126acb63b9f2d5a76ceb1fd331d2b18ae","tid":2039414,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:12:52.000Z","msg":"[文宣方向][跳出同溫層]民意調查分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037458</a>"},{"pid":"0d66131f1b1cc375d2ddd068e25784bf4b4c75e5","tid":2039414,"uid":27898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:12:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />gogogo"},{"pid":"b81961cdb8aebcde83890004f328902d16205ac0","tid":2039414,"uid":62514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />寫事實啫"},{"pid":"d093f55a2c3403d24ca3bb67aa35fc4328bcdca9","tid":2039414,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T04:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm